<br>
Well I got Luclin and tried out human and half elf illusions for the first time since then and hoboy is my illusions very bald. Both of them. So I was wondering if it is safe for me to /face the illusions? Will it affect the enchanters real appearance or...?<br>
<br>
Also about factions. This may make me sound dumb but I really dont know how factions and illusions work. For instance if I do quests that raises the good side but lowers the bad side, will illusions still work? Like for instance if I start hunting in Crushbones and lower my...what ever dark elf faction I happen to lower there, will the dark elf illusion be safe to use in Neriak?<br>
<br>
